<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Privacy Policy — Tabula Poker</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,600;1,400&family=Jost:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    :root {
      --felt: #1a3628;
      --felt-mid: #22402f;
      --gold: #c9a84c;
      --gold-light: #e8c97a;
      --cream: #f5eed8;
      --cream-dim: #c8bc9c;
    }
    body {
      font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;
      background-color: var(--felt);
      color: var(--cream);
      min-height: 100vh;
    }
    body::before {
      content: '';
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      background-image: repeating-linear-gradient(45deg, rgba(0,0,0,0.03) 0px, rgba(0,0,0,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px, transparent 4px);
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    nav {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.15);
    }
    nav a {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-style: italic;
      color: var(--gold-light);
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    nav a:hover { color: var(--cream); }
    main {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      max-width: 680px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 3rem 2rem 5rem;
    }
    h1 {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 3rem);
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--gold-light);
      margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
    }
    .updated {
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      font-weight: 300;
      letter-spacing: 0.15em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--cream-dim);
      opacity: 0.6;
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }
    h2 {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--gold);
      margin-top: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
    }
    p, li {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      font-weight: 300;
      line-height: 1.75;
      color: var(--cream-dim);
    }
    ul {
      padding-left: 1.4rem;
      margin-top: 0.4rem;
    }
    li { margin-bottom: 0.3rem; }
    a { color: var(--gold-light); }
    .divider {
      height: 1px;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, rgba(201,168,76,0.3), transparent);
      margin: 2rem 0;
    }
    .contact-box {
      background: rgba(34,64,47,0.6);
      border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.2);
      padding: 1.5rem;
      margin-top: 2.5rem;
    }
    .contact-box p { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    .contact-box a {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-style: italic;
      color: var(--gold-light);
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <nav><a href="index.html">← Tabula Poker</a></nav>

  <main>
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="updated">Last updated: January 1, 2025</p>

    <p>Tabula Poker ("the App") is developed and maintained by Steelson LLC. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle information when you use the App.</p>

    <div class="divider"></div>

    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>The App itself does not collect any personally identifiable information. However, we use third-party services that may collect data automatically:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Google AdMob</strong> — Used to display advertisements. AdMob may collect device identifiers, IP address, and usage data to serve relevant ads. See <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank">Google's Privacy Policy</a>.</li>
      <li><strong>Apple App Store</strong> — Subject to Apple's privacy practices for app downloads and in-app purchases.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>How We Use Information</h2>
    <p>We do not directly collect, store, or sell personal data. Any data collected by third-party SDKs (e.g., AdMob) is governed by their respective privacy policies and is used for:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Displaying contextually relevant advertisements</li>
      <li>Measuring ad performance</li>
      <li>Fraud prevention</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Advertising</h2>
    <p>The App uses Google AdMob to display ads. You may opt out of personalized advertising by visiting <a href="https://adssettings.google.com" target="_blank">Google Ads Settings</a> or adjusting your device's ad personalization settings in iOS Settings → Privacy → Tracking.</p>

    <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
    <p>The App is not directed at children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children. If you believe a child has provided personal information, please contact us so we can take appropriate action.</p>

    <h2>Data Retention</h2>
    <p>We do not store user data on our servers. Any analytics or advertising data retained by third parties is subject to their own retention policies.</p>

    <h2>Your Rights</h2>
    <p>Depending on your jurisdiction, you may have rights regarding your personal data, including access, correction, deletion, and opt-out of data processing. Contact us for any such requests.</p>

    <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We encourage you to review this page periodically. Continued use of the App after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.</p>

    <div class="divider"></div>

    <div class="contact-box">
      <h2 style="margin-top: 0;">Contact Us</h2>
      <p>For any privacy-related questions or concerns:</p>
      <a href="mailto:support@tato.design">support@tato.design</a>
      <p style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">Steelson LLC</p>
    </div>
  </main>

</body>
</html>
